info.title: AcademicRecordsCWAIM
info.description: This service accesses previous and current Independent Studies and Conferences and Workshops class registration information for an individual, adds Independent Studies or Conferences and Workshops classes for an individual, and modifies grades for Independent Studies or Conferences and Workshops classes for an individual in the AIM System.
